name: Building Upgrades
updated_datetime: '2024-09-07 13:09:26.000000'
---
You can build and upgrade many things in your farm.

When you first buy one of these buildings, crop rows, or the kitchen you get 1 XP for every 1 silver spent. Bonus farming XP perks do not apply to this type of farming XP, however event +XP% bonuses DO apply. After you bought the building, upgrading the storehouse or upgrading productions such as coal or wood DO NOT give XP.

